Crete two nodes in elasticsearch in a single system

1. download elasticsearch and kibana
2. extract the zip files
3. rename elasticsearch folder to node-1
4. create two more folders node-2 and node-3 (with same content as node-1)
5. go to node-1 -> config -> elasticsearch.yml. uncomment the node.name = node-1
