What is Primary term and Sequence number:

primary term: how many times PS has changed (counter)
sequence number: counter for each write operation (PS will increment this counter)

With the help of these we can achieve consistency, and synchronization

Global Check point: a min sequence number of Replication group
Local Check point: a sequence number for a particular shard

