Optimistic Concurrency Control in Elasticsearch

Scenario: assume that in elastic search we store pen details and its stock (10)

1. A read the stock from els -> 10
2. B read the stock from els -> 10
3. A bought the stock -> 10-1 = 9
4. B bought the stock -> 10-1 = 9

Problem: Inconsistency

solution: use primary term, sequence number to achieve consistency

